<h1 class="Article-title">Size</h1>
<p class="Text--lead">Responsive component for determining widths</p>

<p>A utility object that can be combined with other object to determine widths. By default it accommodates up to 10 grid columns. You set different widths for different break points using the responsive modifiers.</p>

